&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work in a fast-paced, multi-disciplinary team to design revolutionary products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the specification, design/selection, qualification and integration of high-performance compute and network modules.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead testing of compute and networking hardware through environmental, power quality, and EMI/EMC qualification campaigns.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
